data.description: Immaculate home w/renovated kitchen and flooring, spacious rooms, level yard w/room for gardening , children play, pet area & more! Natural light throughout , beautiful hardwoods in foyer & ceramic tile in main living areas. This multi level open design home has a specious lower level den w/fireplace for ease of family interaction / entertaining. Situated in an established community with walking trails, swim, and tennis. Neighborhood conveniently located near schools, places of worship, shops, dining.
